snippet.title: VIC20 Cave Command homebrew game
snippet.description:
Action game for the unexpanded VIC20. Intrude the cave. Beware of mines and guided missles. Collect fuel tanks to increase your range.

Game is available for free on Github: https://github.com/HNE74/cbmprogs/tree/master/CaveCommand

Used assembler CbmPrgStudio: https://www.ajordison.co.uk/
